WITH d_rank AS (
    SELECT ListingId, MlsNumber, AddressText, ListingInsertedDateMT, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY AddressText ORDER BY ListingId) drank
    FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]
    WHERE BuildingType = 'House'
)
SELECT *
FROM d_rank
WHERE AddressText = '104 West Creek Court|Chestermere, Alberta T1X1L8'
